title: Rosställispitz
text: The Rosställispitz is a <a href="mountain">mountain</a> of the <a href="Silvretta%20Alps">Silvretta Alps</a>, located west of <a href="Susch">Susch</a> in the canton of <a href="Graub%C3%BCnden">Graubünden</a>. It lies between the valleys of Vereina and Fless, north-east of the <a href="Fl%C3%BCela%20Wisshorn">Flüela Wisshorn</a>.
